== Japanese ==
'''おう''' ([[ō]]) - [[お]] [[う]]

=== Interjection ===
# An informal greeting similar to [[hey]]. See also [[よう]].
#* おう、久しぶりだね - Hey, it's been a long time, eh?
# An informal interjection similar to [[oh]] or [[oops]].
#* おう、しまった! - Oh, no!
# An informal affirmative response.
#* わかった? おう - A: "You see?" B: "Got it."

